---
/* Optional: if you want to pass service data dynamically later,
   you can convert the card list into a JS array. */
---
<!-- Steps Section -->
<section id="steps" class="steps section">

  <!-- Section Title -->
  <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <div><span>How Green Orbit Digital</span> <span class="description-title">Delivers Value</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">

    <div class="steps-wrapper">

      <!-- Step 01 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-lightbulb"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 01</span>
            <h3>Discovery & Insight</h3>
            <p>We begin by understanding your digital environment, organisational goals, audience needs, and sector context. This includes benchmarking digital maturity, identifying growth levers, and uncovering sustainability opportunities. Insights inform strategies that are both effective and responsible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 02 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-gear"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 02</span>
            <h3>Strategy & Design</h3>
            <p>We co-create digital strategies that align with your objectives, integrating sustainable web solutions, SEO, content systems, and analytics frameworks. Every plan is tailored, actionable, and designed to scale, balancing innovation with measurable outcomes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 03 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-bar-chart"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 03</span>
            <h3>Implementation & Collaboration</h3>
            <p>We turn strategy into action, deploying digital platforms, campaigns, automation workflows, and analytics systems. Close collaboration ensures projects run efficiently, delivering measurable growth while reducing environmental impact.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 04 -->
      <div class="step-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="500">
        <div class="step-content">
          <div class="step-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-check2-circle"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="step-info">
            <span class="step-number">Step 04</span>
            <h3>Review, Learn & Scale</h3>
            <p>We embed continuous improvement, optimise digital processes, and scale solutions to achieve long-term impact. Performance insights, user feedback, and sustainability metrics ensure growth is measurable, resilient, and responsible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>
<!-- /Steps Section -->